{
  "texts": [
    "[46] developed a multitask learning framework that utilizes comparable corpora to jointly train the bilingual word embedding and the downstream NER task.",
    "[47] proposed a multitask learning architecture that predicts the labels for both full sentences and individual tokens.",
    "The model aims to learn better language representations and composition functions by combining the objectives at different granularities.In contrast to the above approaches, word segmentation is used as the auxiliary task in this study.",
    "Similarly, [48] proposed a CNN-LSTM-CRF architecture to jointly train Chinese NER and word segmentation models, in which the CNN and Bi-LSTM layers are used to learn hidden representations from local and long-distance contexts, respectively.",
    "Unlike CNN-LSTM-CRF model, we propose a bidirectional dilated causal convolutional neural network (BCNN) to learn hidden representations from both local and long-distance contexts."
  ]
}